snippet.title: Fame City App - Official Trailer by MovieStarPlanet
snippet.description:
Do you want to be the most famous super star of all time? You can in Fame City, the fun role-playing game from MovieStarPlanet.

Download now for iOS: http://bit.ly/1iJKX7J
Download now for Android: http://bit.ly/1f2whRP

Raise your celebrity status to get access to VIP clubs and luxury penthouses. Rub shoulders with cool agents, producers and other celebrities who will help you become a movie legend!


=FEATURES=

- FREE TO PLAY!
- Create celebrity looks from tons of stylish clothes and accessories!
- Win auditions for TV commercials, popular series and block buster films.
- Live the high life with luxury penthouses, access to exclusive clubs and amazing movie sets.
- Meet influential agents and producers in your quest to become super famous
- Collect Fame and StarCoins and transfer to your MovieStarPlanet account

Fame City is a fun way to live like a celebrity. You can dress up like your favourite star and try and become the most famous celebrity in the city.


Impress in auditions and win career breaking roles in the latest block buster, commercial or addictive TV series.


But you can't do it in your own. You will meet influential people on your way, like other celebrities, movie producers and top agents, who will help you rise to become the most famous super star of all time.


It is all part of the journey in Fame City!


Don't forget, you can transfer Fame and StarCoins to MovieStarPlanet -- SO COOL!


PLEASE NOTE: Fame City is completely free to play, however some game items can also be purchased for real money. Fame and StarCoins earned can be transferred to MovieStarPlanet.
